    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a superorder of containing cockroaches, termites, and mantids having two pairs of wings, thickened forewings called tegmina, hindwings folded longitudinally fanwise, hindlegs similar to middle ones that are adapted for running, and mandibulate mouthparts adapted for chewing.</Note_Text>
